{
  "texts": [
    "Models, Datasets, and Implementation.",
    "We finetune LLaMA2-7B, LLaMA2-13B, and LLaMA3.1-8 using MaCP and baseline methods on the Alpaca dataset (Taori et al., 2023).",
    "For evaluation, responses are generated for pre-defined questions from MT-Bench (Zheng et al., 2024) and Vicuna Eval datasets, and scored by GPT-4 on a 10-point scale.",
    "Following prior work (Dettmers et al., 2024 (Dettmers et al.,, 2022)), LoRA, DoRA, and VeRA are applied to all linear layers except the top one, while FourierFT follows the settings in (Gao et al., 2024).",
    "For MaCP, we set n = 700."
  ]
}